title: Filmore and Union - Leeds
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers freshly made food from salads and tagines, to bagels and other foods for breakfast, lunch and dinner. Has a juicing remedy bar. The early dinner menu includes vegan choices. Children and dog friendly. Wi-fi. Part of a chain.
